{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "喪禮", "storyInfo": "被帶進育嬰聖堂的非薩科塔，被告知拉特蘭將為他們賦予光環。一些人試圖反對，卻被強制要求接受光環。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$monastery_sad_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位，就是這裡了，請稍作休息。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我以為，配合調查阿爾圖羅小姐越獄的事情，應該要去公證所或者大教堂。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "帶領二位來的銃騎有事先走了。他託我轉告二位，請不用擔心阿爾圖羅的事情。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一直以來，蘭登修道院的各位都在盡責盡職地守護聖城，我們不會因為一個犯人越獄，就過多苛責。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，那就好那就好。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們請兩位來，是有別的事情要商量。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡好多——", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您希望換個安靜點的地方嗎？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我的意思是，這間育嬰室裡……為什麼全是黎博利？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_367_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1254_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1255_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_comfortbell", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳看向前方，著裝各異的黎博利們或站或坐，沒多少人說話，唯有安撫鈴的聲音穩定地響著。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾百？成千？上萬？席德佳數不清了，或許一整個城市的黎博利都在眼前。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這間育嬰室有這麼大嗎？不，怎樣的場合，需要聚集如此多的黎博利？"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，你們是不是還有一間房裡全是佩洛、一間房裡全是菲林、一間房裡全是魯珀……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您很聰明。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也為墮天使和薩卡茲準備了專門的房間。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呃，您很坦然嘛。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟育嬰聖堂並沒有在做什麼見不得人的事情。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "降生儀式的最後，教皇廳已經宣布，薩科塔將向所有種族分享光環。以種族為單位執行起來是最方便的。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "cr"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.0, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 3.5}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，你是說，我們真的也能擁有光環？也能像薩科塔那樣互相感受？", "name": "黎博利公民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_365_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正如您在降生儀式上感受那隻小木攀獸的心跳。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼呢？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，我為什麼，要擁有光環呢？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "cr", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以說，把我帶到這裡，壓根不是為了梵里妮的事情，而是因為……我是個黎博利？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很快，我也能擁有你頭頂上的這圈日光燈？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "進去吧，潘。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喲，看來我沒有拒絕的權利啊。而且，聽起來是一件大好事，對吧？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起碼對你的眼睛有好處。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不只這樣吧！", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是當初我有光環，是不是就能知道你把吉雅趕出拉特蘭的時候，你那鐵皮腦袋底下是什麼心情了？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道你埋怨我，潘。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很有自知之明。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果沒發生那件事，你或許不會淪落到如今的地步。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭千百年的歷史上，有很多人嘗試過還原典籍中描述的那把恐怖的大口徑轉管遺產銃……成功的只有你。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那種認定使用者能承受遠超常規銃械五倍後座力的設計，真是天才又瘋癲……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，你在沒穿戴銃騎甲胄之前，就成功試驗了我的設計，你是在變相誇自己是天生的銃騎嗎？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當時只覺得自己是你天生的搭檔。你、我、吉雅，從小學到大學，我們一直都是最好的朋友。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我正式成為銃騎的第一項任務，卻是把吉雅驅逐出拉特蘭……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在那之後，你辭去了銃騎專屬製銃師的職務，在我不知道的地方開了一家小工坊，如今又……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是自願退休的，行不行？*拉特蘭俚語*的“製銃聖堂”，要是你們薩科塔都把製銃當作生產洋芋片，那我為什麼還要插手？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是薩科塔有罪，是嗎？吉雅要被趕出去，我要被套上光環……就沒有黎博利能在拉特蘭好好活著？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那件事和吉雅是不是黎博利沒有關係。哪怕她是薩科塔，她感染了礦石病，拉特蘭也不容——", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道個屁！", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不就是什麼“拉特蘭的秩序”、“拉特蘭的純潔”嗎？這些話我從你嘴裡聽過多少次了？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這話你自己信嗎？你想想吉雅是怎麼一個人死在外面的？你*拉特蘭俚語*信嗎？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我承認，我自己曾經相信。直到那個時候，帕特里奇昂……", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們曾一起宿醉，一起玩銃，一起哭一起笑，我們自詡全拉特蘭沒有人的酒杯碰得比我們的響。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但直到吉雅的背影消失在荒野盡頭，你就那麼從我旁邊轉身回拉特蘭的時候，我才意識到……", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們從來沒有真正交流過。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.3, "channel": "cr", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳修女，光環並不是惡物，它是拉特蘭對我們的賜福。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從最初循著馱獸而來的流民開始，黎博利就始終在向薩科塔學習，從生活習慣到思考方式，無所不學。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黎博利嚮往美好的生活，也渴望成為聖城的一部分，我們有目共睹。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不久前，我才剛和阿爾圖羅小姐講過這段歷史。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#3$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但唯有薩科塔頭頂上的光環，黎博利怎麼都無法習得。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也正因為如此，一直以來，薩科塔與生活在拉特蘭的其他種族之間，始終都存在一些無法調和的矛盾。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們無從參與薩科塔的共感，你們會苦惱自己的信仰是否毫無根基，你們會質疑拉特蘭的冷漠與疏離……", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳修女，您此前為了解決蘭登修道院的財務危機，常年不在拉特蘭，所以對這種情況缺乏一些認知。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您可以再去問問其他的黎博利……", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#11$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道在這裡生活的很多異族人都羡慕你們的共感。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#2$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以接下來，我們將向每一個人分享它。它會讓我們不再有誤會、不再有分歧，讓我們真正理解彼此，消弭矛盾和隔閡……", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓黎博利，真正成為拉特蘭不可分割的一部分。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只覺得難過。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從小在這座城市長大，知道哪家店做的甜點不甜，哪條巷子的流浪雲獸愛吃南瓜，哪棟樓的天台適合看星星。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在蘭登修道院的日子，我和薩科塔修女們一起釀啤酒做麵包，分頭跑到其他國家拉贊助，又在回來聚會的時候喝得酩酊大醉……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我偷拍她們睡覺時翅膀穿過椅背的滑稽樣子，她們在我偷溜出去的時候在教堂裡放安眠曲，好讓主教睡得更久一點……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，席德佳，我還記得。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實主教早就發現了，他只是捨不得責怪你。", "name": "緊張的修女"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_370_1#1$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，我是個拉特蘭人。我很喜歡這裡，很喜歡很喜歡。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說得沒錯，我確實很多時候都發現自己在狀況外，我不懂為什麼在同僚的葬禮上，薩科塔們哭著哭著就笑著唱起了歌……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我爸爸是個獵戶，每年冬天，他都會和其他人結伴，進山打獵。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他告訴我，哪怕是相處了十幾年的老夥伴，也會在發現同一個獵物時有不同的意見，甚至吵起來。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人和人本來就是不一樣的，這和我們有沒有光環沒有關係。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是您剛剛跟我說，我要獲得光環，才能真正成為拉特蘭的一分子。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您是在說，我過去二十多年，都不算是一個真正的拉特蘭人？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是在說，我所有的生活，都只是一種不夠完美的模仿？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實如此，席德佳修女，但這並不是對您或其他任何黎博利的否定。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這只是一種必要的，對拉特蘭的肯定。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保育員先生，我不在乎什麼否定和肯定。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不覺得我和我的生活有什麼錯。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不覺得自己有什麼理由要接受這種所謂的“賜福”。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#15$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1788_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1789_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loading_intro", "key": "$loading_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是拉特蘭的決定，席德佳修女。", "name": "保育員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1786_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是我第一次感受到離別的滋味，潘。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……十分難受。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，從那時開始，我的人生就開始不對勁了。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像那種爆米花電影，哈哈，《電鋸俠》系列，或者《藍橋遺夢》系列，一個橋段成了經典，開始反反覆覆地出現。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吉雅之後是你，再後來是我最器重的學生，基於某些原因，我親手將她驅逐出拉特蘭。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有小菲，也讓人很頭痛……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼？你還擔心哪天你的孫女跑了，自己變成孤寡老人？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們有各自的問題，我嘗試過做些什麼，但好像什麼都做不了。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那是嘗試，還是自我欺騙、自我安慰？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許都是吧。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過你剛剛說錯了一件事，希望每一個人都擁有光環，並不僅僅是為了守護所謂“聖城的秩序和純潔”……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說得好像拉特蘭是個有種族潔癖的國家一樣。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "共享光環的拉特蘭，將成為一個真正的整體，連某種無從想像的、威脅全泰拉的災厄都能夠解決。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那樣的拉特蘭，自然也能夠解決我們所遭遇的一切問題，包括……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，談心時間結束。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "*拉特蘭俚語*，你終於說完了。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又一次從你嘴裡聽到這些鬼話，真噁心。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘，進去吧。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我拒絕呢？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才不想要你頭頂那個發光的東西，我對理解你的苦心一點興趣都沒有。", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sldrpllgn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘格尼尼向銃騎舉起了自己手中的銃。"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再等等吧。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "潘格尼尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1781_1#3$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我承認你是個天才的製銃師，但你是個黎博利，潘。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒辦法使用自己親手打造的這些銃。它們在你手裡，只是一張張名片。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你真的對我那麼不滿，真的想要賞我一顆子彈，你就應該等到儀式結束。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到了那時，你擁有了光環，也就擁有了使用它的資格——", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_speardrop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_maskbreak", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.2}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘格尼尼重重地將銃砸在銃騎的甲胄上，碎屑紛飛，斷裂的銃托摔了出去，沉悶的嗡響自遠處傳來，在走廊裡久久迴盪。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot",